TEXT.S:
Bujar Nishani
u siwkay 9 bulad 29 demiad, Bujar Nishani, u misingkiway. 1966 a mihcan nalecuhan. u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Albania ayza sa ci Bujar Nishani, micakat a demiad sa i 2012 a mihcan 7 bulad 24 demiad.
u sulit nu zuma a kamu u sulit nu Hulam: ··2012714073 maala ciniza i 2017.7 u tapang nu kanatal, i sinkiw kya tapang nu kanatal, maala 73 paya' i labu' nu 140. u sulit nu Amilika: Bujar Nishani is an Albanian politician who was President of Albaniafrom 24 July 2012 to 24 July 2017. u sulit nu Lipun: 201271
